title: East 17th Street Ep . 42 Previewing the 2025 Big Ten Championship
body_text:
Following some quick IU basketball talk, Mike Schumann and Seth Tow of The Daily Hoosier preview the 2025 Big Ten Championship featuring No. 2 Indiana vs. No. 1 Ohio State.
You can find previous episodes of East 17th Street by GOING HERE.
You can also find East 17th Street at your favorite podcast directories including Apple Podcasts, Spotify, and Amazon Music.
